    <item>
      <title>Janus 和 Columbia 关注选举前沉重的抵押贷款债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/janus-columbia-eye-beaten-down-mortgage-debt-ahead-of-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券市场动荡加剧以及对美国通胀上升的担忧对机构抵押贷款债券的打击尤为严重。对于 Janus Henderson 和 Columbia Threadneedle Investments 的投资者来说，这种疲软可能为购买这些证券提供了机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/janus-columbia-eye-beaten-down-mortgage-debt-ahead-of-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 14:29:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音公司启动 190 亿美元股票出售计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-28/boeing-launches-19-billion-share-sale-to-stave-off-downgrade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波音公司周一启动了一项价值近 190 亿美元的股票出售计划，出售 9000 万股普通股和约 50 亿美元的存托股票，以解决这家陷入困境的飞机制造商的流动性需求。彭博电视台的 Sid Philip 报道了这一消息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-28/boeing-launches-19-billion-share-sale-to-stave-off-downgrade</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 14:09:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚德尼认为，随着美国和英国准备发行债券，债券义警正在集结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/yardeni-sees-bond-vigilantes-mustering-as-us-uk-prep-debt-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街资深人士埃德·亚德尼 (Ed Yardeni) 表示，随着美国财政部准备好新的债务发行计划，即将到来的美国大选可能预示着市场债券义勇军的回归。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/yardeni-sees-bond-vigilantes-mustering-as-us-uk-prep-debt-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 13:53:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Azul 股价因与债权人达成新融资协议而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/azul-inks-deals-with-bondholders-for-500-million-in-financing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西航空公司 Azul SA 与其债券持有人签署协议后，其股价大幅上涨，该协议允许其与租赁商和零部件供应商推进一项重要交易，从而减少该航空公司的债务并增强其现金状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/azul-inks-deals-with-bondholders-for-500-million-in-financing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 12:48:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Cemex 因盈利不及预期、前景下调而跌至 2020 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/cemex-sales-miss-estimates-as-bad-weather-hits-us-and-mexico</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥水泥制造商 Cemex SAB 下调了今年的业绩预期，并公布第三季度净收入低于预期，导致股价出现 2020 年以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/cemex-sales-miss-estimates-as-bad-weather-hits-us-and-mexico</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 10:18:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国财报最繁忙的一周伊始，股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/yen-drops-as-japan-election-unnerves-investors-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在企业财报发布最为繁忙的一周中，股市开始上涨，交易员们也为三份备受瞩目的经济报告做准备，这些报告将为美联储的下一次决策奠定基础。油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/yen-drops-as-japan-election-unnerves-investors-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 22:34:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列限制伊朗袭击军事目标 油价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/brent-falls-5-at-open-after-israel-strikes-avoid-iranian-crude</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周初，以色列对伊朗目标的袭击避开了该欧佩克成员国的原油设施，这增加了该地区敌对状态可能缓和的可能性，导致油价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/brent-falls-5-at-open-after-israel-strikes-avoid-iranian-crude</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 22:03:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
